'''Spritzer''' was the informal name attributed to a gelatinous fluid used to entangle prey. In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], the weapons dealer [[Orion Ferret]] used a quantity of spritzer to ensnare the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] inside of his private office on the [[Space station/Legends|space station]] [[Bazarre]]. Although the spritzer in question was quite dense, it was not strong enough to keep Chewbacca imprisoned for long. Within minutes, the Wookiee was able to claw his way free of the chemical mass and apprehend Ferret.

